/datum/faith/forces
	name = "The Faerûn's Forces"
	desc = "The Faerûn's Forces is a faith that honors the myriad powerful entities beyond the mortal realm, from the capricious Archfey to the malevolent Fiends and the ancient elemental beings. Followers believe that these entities, though often unpredictable and dangerous, hold great power and influence over the world. The Forces are not bound by morality; they are forces of nature, raw power, and ancient bargains. Those who worship them seek to harness their might, be it through pacts, worship, or aligning with their will, for the promise of power, knowledge, or survival in a world shaped by these otherworldly powers."
	worshippers = "Anyone, literally anyone."
	godhead = /datum/patron/forces/asmodeus
